text: Moimenta may refer to the following places in Portugal: * Moimenta da Beira, a municipality in the district of Viseu * Moimenta (Cinfães), a civil parish in the municipality of Cinfães * Moimenta (Terras de Bouro), a civil parish in the municipality of Terras de Bouro * Moimenta (Vinhais), a civil parish in the municipality of Vinhais * Moimenta da Serra, a civil parish in the municipality of Gouveia * Moimenta de Maceira Dão, a civil parish in the municipality of Mangualde
title: Moimenta
